OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA fatal train crash could have been
OL,8,Favoided if a driver had used an
OL,9,Femergency system designed to reduce
OL,10,Fspeed, an investigation by the Rail
OL,11,FAccident Investigation Branch (RAIB)
OL,12,Fhas found.
OL,14,FPassenger David Tudor Evans, 66, died
OL,15,F"as a consequence" and four others
OL,16,Fwere seriously injured when two
OL,17,FTransport for Wales (TfW) trains
OL,18,Fcollided in mid Wales on 21 October,
OL,19,F2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt was Britain's first fatal crash
OL,8,Finvolving multiple trains in more than
OL,9,F25 years.
OL,11,FThe report has made nine
OL,12,Frecommendations to four organisations:
OL,13,FTfW, the Rail Safety and Standards
OL,14,FBoard, Angel Trains and Network Rail.
OL,16,FThe collision happened near Talerddig
OL,17,Fin Powys on a rural section of the
OL,18,FCambrian line, which is predominantly
OL,19,Fsingle track with loops to allow
OL,20,Ftrains travelling in opposite
OL,21,Fdirections to pass each other.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHowever, despite breaking, a westbound
OL,8,FTfW train failed to stop as intended
OL,9,Finside a loop, rejoining the single
OL,10,Fline too soon and crashing into
OL,11,Fanother oncoming TfW train.
OL,13,FThe RAIB said the intended stop never
OL,14,Fhappened because the westbound train's
OL,15,Fwheels were sliding, which can be an
OL,16,Fissue in the autumn when fallen leaves
OL,17,Fcan makes tracks slippery.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FTo provide extra grip when needed, the
OL,8,Fclass 158 trains involved in the crash
OL,9,Fhave two systems - one automatic and
OL,10,Fone manual - to dispense sand between
OL,11,Fwheels and rails.
OL,13,FThe RAIB revealed in an interim report
OL,14,Fin April last year that the westbound
OL,15,Ftrain's automatic system did not work
OL,16,Fin the moments before the crash
OL,17,Fbecause of several failures.
OL,19,FThe full report published today also
OL,20,Fsaid that the driver did not activate
OL,21,Fthe manually operated emergency sander.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FInvestigators calculated that the
OL,8,Ftrain would have stopped within the
OL,9,Floop as planned if the manual sander
OL,10,Fwas used when its emergency brake was
OL,11,Factivated.
OL,13,FThe RAIB say the slippery conditions,
OL,14,Fthe failure of the automatic system
OL,15,Fand the driver not activating the
OL,16,Fmanual system all contributed to the
OL,17,Fcrash.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"This accident does require all three
OL,8,Fof those very different factors to be
OL,9,Fin place on the night - withdraw any
OL,10,Fof those factors and the accident
OL,11,Fsimply doesn't happen," Mark Hamilton,
OL,12,Fan inspector for the RAIB told ITV
OL,13,FCymru Wales.
OL,15,F"It is a combination of those three
OL,16,Fthings makes it quite a rare accident
OL,17,Fbut still very tragic and difficult
OL,18,Ffor all the people it has touched."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe RAIB said a rule book for TfW
OL,8,Fdrivers states they should deploy the
OL,9,Femergency sander "when a train is
OL,10,Funable to stop in the usual distance"
OL,11,Fand its use may avoid a collision.
OL,13,FHowever, the driver, who was not
OL,14,Fidentified in the report, "did not
OL,15,Frecall any training on the use of
OL,16,Femergency sanders and had not
OL,17,Fpreviously needed to use them while
OL,18,Fdriving," the report said.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe driver said that "it had not
OL,8,Foccurred to them to use the emergency
OL,9,Fsanders on the day of the accident"
OL,10,Fand that they believed adhesion
OL,11,Fconditions would improve based on
OL,12,Ftheir previous experiences.
OL,14,FTransport for Wales said the driver
OL,15,Fwas fully trained and had completed
OL,16,Fall courses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe westbound train, on which Mr Evans
OL,8,Fwas a passenger, travelled
OL,9,Fapproximately 1,080 metres (0.7 miles)
OL,10,Fbeyond its intended stopping position
OL,11,Fbefore the collision.
OL,13,FIt was moving at about 24mph when the
OL,14,Fcrash happened, while the other train
OL,15,Fwas travelling at about 6mph.
OL,17,FThe report's nine recommendations are
OL,18,Faimed at reducing the likelihood and
OL,19,Fmitigating the consequences of a
OL,20,Fsimilar event, including calling for
OL,21,FTfW to review how drivers are trained.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,438,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"The recommendations are intended
OL,8,Fentirely to change the way that the
OL,9,Findustry approaches the areas we've
OL,10,Fmade recommendations in, so we're
OL,11,Freally hopeful some meaningful change
OL,12,Fwill come about," Mr Hamilton said.
OL,14,FAndrew Hall, the RAIB's chief
OL,15,Finspector of rail accidents, described
OL,16,Fthe Talerddig crash as "a tragedy".
OL,26,@xD@XOUxD@bO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/15
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
