PN,43715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781894898
OL,3,CTrain driver did not use emergency
OL,4,Csystem during fatal collision, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"We welcome the recommendations in the
OL,8,Freport and will assist their
OL,9,Fimplementation to ensure incidents
OL,10,Flike this become even rarer on Wales's
OL,11,Frailway."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]
